completed.thoughts: I love Halo, but this never really came close to the lowest of my expectations. It’s a shame it missed the mark, there is so much lore that they just constantly bungled.

completed.title: Star Trek

completed.title: Star Trek: Deep Space Nine
completed.thoughts: This by far is my favorite Star Trek series. The way the characters are developed is amazing and there are so many great stories within the series. It was also the first Star Trek series to have a full storyline.

completed.title: Star Trek: Discovery
completed.thoughts: The show had its ups and downs. I enjoyed most of the stories and its characters. It’s a shame it had to end so soon.

completed.title: Star Trek: Enterprise
completed.thoughts: I recently watched this again with my wife. It reminded me how much it sucked that it was cancelled after only 4 seasons. They could've done so much more. The first two seasons were shaky, but it finished strong and was still a good series.

completed.title: Star Trek: Picard
completed.thoughts: The 3rd season was definitely the best. So much nostalgia with a good story. I enjoyed the first 2 seasons, but they didn't match what season 3 brought to the screen.

completed.title: Star Trek: The Next Generation
completed.thoughts: The quintessential Star Trek. It was an amazing series that I constantly get more out of everytime I re-watch it

completed.thoughts: I enjoyed this series. They could have done more with the stranded part making it a little more rough, but the cast and series worked well.
